  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Good continental buffet breakfast included, taken in the hotel.</li>
<li>The optional good-value half board set menu is taken in a nearby 'Vieux Valais' restaurant (20m from hotel) and can be pre-booked at a supplement from £20 per person per night (please add at time of booking).</li>
<li>Please note special dietary requirements cannot be catered for.</li>
<li>Half board if pre-booked is a SET menu at restaurant 'Vieux Valais' a popular Italian restaurant offering a selection of antipasti including carpaccio and smoked salmon pasta dishes, salads, soups including minestrone, tomato and lobster bisque, risottos, meat and fish dishes and an extensive pizza menu.</li>
<li>Sample Menu: Minestrone or Mixed Salad, Entrecote of beef with vegetable and fries, Tiramisu.</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>In a convenient position just 2 minutes’ walk from Zermatt’s main street and Gornergrat rack railway for access to the skiing, the Atlanta is a simple, good-value accommodation choice for those wanting a relaxed atmosphere with good access to all this fantastic resort has to offer. Alternatively, the ski bus for the Matterhorn Glacier Paradise gondola stops just 2 minutes' walk from the hotel and is free with your lift pass. For a well-earned drink after a day's skiing, Zermatt's legendary après-ski and nightlife is round the corner. Our prices are based on bed and breakfast with an excellent value, half board option, taken in the restaurant 'Vieux Valais' 20m from the hotel, available to pre-book.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
